			<p>I was going to let my <em>Sun</em> subscription expire and concentrate more on my own writing until I read Kelly DeLong&rsquo;s unflinching and marvelous memoir of personal redemption [&ldquo;<a href="/article/4427">My First Date</a>,&rdquo; June 2010]. To think I might have missed that! My check is in the mail.</p>
							<p class="quote-2-author">Mary Dittoe Kelly<br></p>
