							<h6 class="b-content-section heading-square heading-border"><a href="/sections/fiction">Fiction</a></h6>
		

				<h3 class="block-content-title"><a href="/issues/354/the-view-from-here-354">The View From Here</a></h3>
					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle"></p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li>
							By <a class="meta-article-contributors" href="/contributors/mithran-somasundrum">Mithran Somasundrum</a></li><li><a href="/issues/354">June 2005</a></li></ul>

		

